data.description: Welcome home to Timberwilde!!  Enjoy a well-maintained, carpet-free, updated home on an oversized lot (70x120) with mature trees and overzized covered patio and storage workshop.  Conveniently located in The Great Northwest (Culebra & Grissom):  this home has all the classic design elements with splashes of modern updates to get you settled into a well-established neighborhood and access to many amenities & shopping, and restaurants. ***Charming 2 Story w/Primary Down 3 bed/2.5 bath/2-Garage, 3-sided Brick, Wood and Gas start fireplace, ATTIC storage goes through stairs around house. Assumable VA 2.625 FIXED***, apply with current lender to assume terms of loan: Rocket Mortgage 800# or apply online. Seller has updated the kitchen with recessed lighting, some new windows, new cabinets w/hardware, Quartz countertops (with a warranty) & stainless steel appliances, tile backsplash, and pot-filler. Whole house interior and exterior paint 2024, gutters, Water heater 2016, Roof 2017, Elmer's installed HVAC 7/2021 with uv lamp, H20 softener installed 2022. Google Fiber and doorbell with monitor, covered patio with recessed lights and fan perfect for BBQ outing! NISD schools and public bus stop, public library & HEB, Walmart grocery nearby.
